value.text: For sequences of entities where the next one replaced the previous one: political offices, hereditary titles, states and administrative entities... Use in combination with replaces (P1365). For buildings, rather use structure replaces (P1398). Can be used as qualifier on a statement describing a sequence. If item is last in a series, value type for this property should be "no value", rather than a value of "last" (Q30013662),, which is ambiguous. (English)
